\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What\u8217\'92d I say about flappin\u8217\'92 them lips? How\u8217\'92d you figure that meant you could spit piss in my general direction?\u8221\'94 Bib tsked at Mandri\u8217\'92s insolence. \u8220\'93You break the rules you get what\u8217\'92s comin. That\u8217\'92s how it be in the Ayramun.\u8221\'94}
